EIOPA’s Bernardino Says EU Agency Has Done Crisis Exercise

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-10-04T15:21:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/eiopa-s-bernardino-says-eu-agency-has-done-crisis-exercise.html
Gabriel Bernardino, chairman of the
European Insurance and Occupational Pensions Authority, said the
agency has recently “simulated a crisis exercise.”  This included testing of contacts with national
supervisors, he said at the European Parliament in Brussels
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
